  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed; required levels are met or exceeded at each factor. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed and all credibility factor gaps have been resolved. Decision: Accepted. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the structured Context of Use object is captured in the associated Claim and Requirement prose rather than as a discrete hasContextOfUse node.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-experimental-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-hemolysis-bench-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/monte-carlo-uq-samples-vad"
  ],
